description: KebNi AB engages in the development, manufacture, marketing, and trading of satellite and communication equipment. The company is headquartered in Kista, Stockholm. The company went IPO on 2014-01-29. KebNi AB, via the KebNi Maritime brand, develops, manufactures and sells 4-axes that stabilize VSAT antennas for maritime use based on a P9 antenna platform. KebNi Inertial Sensing AB develops, manufactures and sells inertial sensors designed to measure movements in three dimensions. KebNi Land Mobile AB develops, manufactures and sells Communication on the Move (COTM) antennas for land. Satmission AB develops, manufactures and sells Communication on the Pause (COTP) for mobile satellite communication systems.
naicsNationalIndustry: Radio and Television Broadcasting and Wireless Communications Equipment Manufacturing
